&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for an Associate Data Scientist to help turn complex data into clear, actionable business decisions. You&#39;ll develop predictive models using statistical and machine learning techniques, analyze large datasets to surface meaningful patterns, and partner with cross-functional teams to design data-driven solutions. You&#39;ll communicate findings through clear visualizations and reports, stay current on emerging data science techniques, and help bring your work to life through web interfaces and API deployments. This is a great opportunity for someone early in their data science career looking to build hands-on experience across the full lifecycle, from modeling to deployment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;Develop predictive models using statistical and deep machine learning algorithms to solve business problems&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Analyze large and somewhat complex data sets to identify patterns and insights that drive key business decisions&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to design data-driven solutions that meet business objectives&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Communicate results and insights to stakeholders through visualizations and reports that are easy to understand&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Review the latest developments in data science and machine learning techniques, and continuously improve the organization’s analytical capabilities

