&lt;p&gt;Reporting to our Director of Renewals, the Renewal Manager is a critical role responsible for driving commercial contract excellence and client retention (GRR) across Billtrust customers. You will manage the end-to-end renewal process - from strategy creation through contract signature - for a territory of assigned accounts, working closely with Sales and Customer Success. You will partner cross-functionally with Legal, Deal Desk, Finance/Accounting, Product, and SalesOps to ensure on-time, quality contracts, value-anchored renewal conversations, and positive overall client experience. As a Renewal Manager, you will identify, escalate, and mitigate renewal risk early/often – and keep renewal opportunity data updated and accurate in Salesforce. We are elevating the overall role of our Renewals team this year by moving to a proactive, strategic support model – and you will play a major part of our success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Theme 1: Proactive Renewal Execution &amp;amp; Commercial Excellence&lt;/p&gt;
